  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "P.U.N.K. JAM FEVER!",
      "effect": "2 Level 8 monsters\nOnce per turn, you can also Xyz Summon \"P.U.N.K. JAM FEVER!\" by using 1 \"P.U.N.K.\" Fusion or Synchro Monster you control as material. You can only use each of the following effects of \"P.U.N.K. JAM FEVER!\" once per turn. You can pay 600 LP and detach 1 material from this card; draw 1 card. When another monster's effect is activated and you have a Level 3 Psychic monster in your GY (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that monster.",
      "official": false
    },
